President Muhammadu Buhari Thursday signed the 2021 Appropriation Bill into law. The appropriation bill, with a total budget of N13, 588, 027,886, 175 trillion, was signed into law at the Council Chamber of the State House Abuja., The signing ceremony was witnessed by Vice President Yemi Osinbajo, Senate President Ahmad Lawan, Speaker, House of Representatives, Femi Gbajabiamila, Secretary to the Government of the Federation (SGF), Mr. Boss Mustapha and Minister of Finance, Budget and National Planning, Mrs. Zainab Ahmed, among others. See images. <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478993" src="https://i2.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/9ea8270d-pmb-signs-2021-appropriation-bill-0004.jpg?resize=611%2C407&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="611" height="407" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478992" src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/bff1c06d-pmb-signs-2021-appropriation-bill-0001-2.jpg?resize=605%2C403&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="605" height="403" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478996" src="https://i2.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/8614572b-fb_img_1609443574028.jpg?resize=596%2C397&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="596" height="397" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478994" src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/030dfa46-pmb-signs-2021-appropriation-bill-0006.jpg?resize=609%2C406&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="609" height="406" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478997" src="https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/thisday-846548948316-wp-data/wp-media/a63cd495-fb_img_1609443581956.jpg?resize=599%2C399&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="599" height="399" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone  wp-image-478999" src="https://i0.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com